The '''1984 Monte Carlo Open''' (also known as the '''Jacomo Monte Carlo Open''' for sponsorship reasons) was a men's [[tennis]] tournament played on [[Clay court|outdoor clay courts]] at the [[Monte Carlo Country Club]] in [[Monte Carlo]], [[Monaco]] that was part of the [[1984 Volvo Grand Prix]]. The tournament was held from 16 April through 20 April 1984.

==Champions==

===Singles===
{{main|1984 Monte Carlo Open – Singles}}
{{flagicon|SWE}} '''[[Henrik Sundström]]''' defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Mats Wilander]], 6–3, 7–5, 6–2

===Doubles===
{{main|1984 Monte Carlo Open – Doubles}}
{{flagicon|AUS}} '''[[Mark Edmondson]]''' / {{flagicon|USA}} '''[[Sherwood Stewart]]''' defeated {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Jan Gunnarsson]] / {{flagicon|SWE}} [[Mats Wilander]], 6–2, 6–1.

